						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone near the sībārakaṭṭe.</hi></p>						

						<p>A.D. 1414.</p>						

						<p>This inscription dated in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1336, Jaya, Śrāvaṇa śu. Tuesday</hi> records the grant of land given as <hi rend="italic">nettarugeyi</hi> to the family of a certain <hi rend="bold">Hobbaya,</hi> who died in a fight in <hi rend="bold">Tiraḷigeṟe.</hi> The details of the date correspond to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1414, August 24 or 31.</hi> The given week-day (<hi rend="italic">i.e.,</hi> Tuesday) occurred twice in the fortnight.</p>						

						</summary>
